Package org.ejbca.core.model.ra

Class ExtendedInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.internal.UpgradeableDataHashMap
      • org.ejbca.core.model.ra.ExtendedInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, IUpgradeableData
    public class ExtendedInformation
extends UpgradeableDataHashMap
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    Deprecated.
    Use org.cesecore.certificates.endentity.ExtendedInformation instead. Deprecated since EJBCA 5.0.0
    The model representation of Exended Information about a user. It's used for non-searchable data about a user, like a image, in an effort to minimize the need for database alterations NOTE! This class is not to be extended anymore. It is kept for backwards serialization compatibility only. use class org.cesecore.certificates.endentity.ExtendedInformation instead.
    Version:
